    <item>
      <title>随着火灾担忧加剧，加州允许将再保险成本计入保费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/california-allows-reinsurance-cost-in-rates-as-fire-worry-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州批准了新规定，允许保险公司在制定费率时考虑再保险成本，这是监管改革的最后一项重要举措，旨在阻止在人们对野火的担忧日益加剧之际保险公司大批撤离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/california-allows-reinsurance-cost-in-rates-as-fire-worry-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 21:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克劳迪娅·萨姆称劳动力市场风险大于通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/labor-market-a-bigger-risk-than-inflation-claudia-sahm-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[New Century Advisors 首席经济学家 Claudia Sahm 表示，她更关心劳动力市场而不是通货膨胀，她认为目前通货膨胀“还好”。她在彭博电视台与 Matt Miller 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-30/labor-market-a-bigger-risk-than-inflation-claudia-sahm-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 20:22:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管央行施压，巴西雷亚尔年内仍暴跌 21%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/brazil-leads-global-losses-in-2024-as-fiscal-angst-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西资产今年的表现落后于所有主要货币，由于人们对总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 解决不断膨胀的预算赤字的承诺越来越怀疑，雷亚尔创下了 2020 年疫情冲击以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/brazil-leads-global-losses-in-2024-as-fiscal-angst-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将百威英博俄罗斯子公司的控制权移交给当地公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已将百威英博合资企业的控制权交给了一家当地公司，此举打乱了百威英博通过与土耳其合作伙伴达成协议退出俄罗斯的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
